---
title: Creamy Prawn Linguine with fresh basil and chilli flakes
description: If you're looking for a filling and familiar meal to warm you up on these cold winter evenings, then a big bowl of pasta is always a winner. This particular pasta dish features linguine—spaghetti's slightly flatter friend—along with a creamy tomato sauce and perfectly cooked prawns.
